video_info.title: WATCH: Trump FULL SPEECH in Michigan, first rally since assassination attempt | LiveNOW FOX
video_info.description:
Former President Donald Trump and his newly announced vice president running mate JD Vance held their first campaign rally together in Grand Rapids, Michigan for the 2024 election. It's the first rally since a week ago where Trump survived an assassination attempt in Butler, PA. Trump's speech lasted nearly two hours, and Vance spoke as well at length, who introduced the former president personally.
